  <style>

      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533777857889-4be7c70b33f7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80') no-repeat center center/cover;
      height: 500px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px #000;
    }

      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .menu-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      background: #f7f2ee;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .menu-item img {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .menu-item div {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    form {
      background: #f7f2ee;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    form input, form select, form textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.7rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    form button {
      background-color: #4b3225;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    footer {
      background-color: #2e1f15;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .qr {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .qr img {
      width: 150px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

  <div class="section" id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Founded by passionate law students, Coffee and Counsel blends warm hospitality with legal accessibility. Based in a fully furnished 1200 sq. ft. space in Kolkata, it serves not only high-quality food and beverages but also delivers free legal consultations to empower the community.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="legal-help">
    <h2>Legal Help Desk</h2>
    <p>We offer approachable legal support inside the café — free of charge. Discuss daily-life disputes, tenant issues, property conflicts, work grievances, and marital problems in a safe, casual setting.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="order">
    <h2>Place Your Order</h2>
    <form>
      <label for="name">Full Name</label>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

      <label for="order">Your Order</label>
      <textarea id="order" name="order" rows="4" placeholder="Example: 1 x Freedom Bite, 2 x Peace Fries" required></textarea>

      <label for="contact">Contact Number</label>
      <input type="tel" id="contact" name="contact" required>

      <button type="submit">Submit Order</button>
    </form>

    <div class="qr">
      <h3>Scan to Pay</h3>
      <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://coffeeandcounsel.com/fake-payment" alt="QR Code for Payment">
      <p><em>(Note: This is a placeholder QR for mock-up use)</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="vision">
    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p>We aim to break the fear around legal spaces by making them casual, friendly, and accessible. Whether you're a tea vendor, student, or homemaker — your voice matters, your rights matter. Over coffee, let’s talk law and build clarity.</p>
  </div>
